(2515, 409, 'photo_booth_rental_content', '<h3>Have You Thought About a Party Photo Booth for Your New York Event?</h3>\r\nIt\'s always good when you can offer your guests something different and engaging; even better if you can provide them with a permanent memento of your event. To achieve both these aims, a growing number of party planners are recognizing the value which hiring a party photo booth can bring. Not only is a photo booth a great opportunity to obtain fantastic pictures, the prints can serve as a permanent reminder of a fun packed party or other occasion.\r\n<h3>Fantastic Marketing Opportunity</h3>\r\nIf your party is a corporate one, or even if you just want to share a unique greeting with your guests, we have the ideal solution. The prints from our photo booths can be customized to include your corporate logo or an individually tailored piece of text. This appears on every picture, giving you the perfect opportunity to spread your message. Why not take advantage of our scrap book opportunity to display your prints in an attractive way that\'s always appealing?\r\n<h3>Multiple Prints for All</h3>\r\nIt\'s always disappointing when a number of people have crowded together to get their picture taken, only to find that there\'s only one copy of the results. To solve this problem, we\'ve customized our booths so that you can alter the number of prints to suit your individual requirements. This means that everyone has the chance to benefit from a high quality copy of their chosen picture.\r\n<h3>We Can Take the Booth to You, Wherever You Are in New York</h3>\r\nBecause our booths can be partially disassembled, they can be used in a wide variety of locations, including those which aren\'t particularly accessible. We can successfully transport our booths up stairs and through narrow doorways, providing an engaging opportunity for party fun anywhere in the city. To find out more or to book one of our booths, call us now at <a href=\"tel:8883409190\">(888) 340-9190</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTo make your event look more glamorous and memorable, photographs play an important role, and nowadays conventional photography is out of fashion. People prefer open style kiosks which can be set up anywhere at the venue as a photography studio. If you need an elegant and affordable Photo booth rental NY contact ISH photoboothrentals for well-designed kiosks, with solid walls and proper seating (in case you are choosing the elite type kiosk) and other facilities. The quality of the photograph taken by our Photo booth rental NY, are the best and almost 6-12 people can be accommodated in one for a great get together. All you need to is to hire a New York Photo Booth Rental, as per your requirement choose the kiosk type and get ready for some awesome capturing of important moments in the event. We take immense pride in the innovation and dependability of our NYC photo booths.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn case you face any problem while doing that, take help form the attendants standing by. After that, choose the photos you like from the lot taken from the Photo booth NY or download it from the password protected gallery in the internet. They get uploaded in no time by the company for your ready reference! So now you too can make your party a grand event with our Photo booth NY services. Our NYC photo booth rental services, brings an instantaneous glamour factor to your special event.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe are your local services providers for Photo booth rental NY, CT, NJ and Long Island areas. Our photo booths are well-designed to fit your needs and capture best quality images and videos to add that extra flair to your event.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTo reserve a Photo booth rental NY and capture your most precious moments contact us at sales@ishphotoboothrentals.com. Photo Booth Rental Services New York has never been easier!\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h2>A Modern Way To Gain A Glamorous Appeal</h2>\r\n</div>\r\nTo enjoy the real fun of an event one need to plan and organize a few things perfectly. Whether you are planning to organize a birthday party, product launch, wedding event or an anniversary, we support you by providing the photo booth rental NY.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul class=\"content-list\">\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> We capture the finest moments of your life and present it in a much glamorous way at an affordable range. Our professionals use the modern technology and latest equipment which turns a snap to be of great quality and good clarity.</li>\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> We provide the photo booth rentals New York, which will stand as a compliment to your party. Our booths capture hundreds of photos and even the help of a special feature you can get unlimited prints.</li>\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> Our specialty is that we offer high definition prints of your photographs and with several backgrounds and solid colors. No matter what your venue, we provide the best experience of the photo booth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWith an aim to support you by providing a chance to collect the marvelous snaps of the mesmerizing events. We even mail all the heart melt pictures to all your guests through the photo booth NY which makes everyone feel happy and talk regarding your party or the event for a very long time.\r\n<h3>Throw A Party No New Yorker Will Forget</h3>\r\nMost people who visit New York would agree that the obvious tourist destinations are memorable and are on the “to-do” list, but one thing they didn’t prepare for were the people. The people and the crowds are what help New York to feel so alive, which is why most visitors bring a camera. Not just for the buildings and the scenery, but for all the unusual fashions, performances and culture.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBut if you live in New York, the crowds and unique personalities are nothing new, so how do you make your next event feel special for New Yorkers and out-of-towners alike? If you’re hosting a party, corporate meeting or fundraiser where you’re expecting out-of-towners, you may want to think about supplying the cameras. And no we don’t mean the disposable ones from the nineties. A great way for your guests to remember your fundraiser or event is through a photo booth rental.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOur selection of photo booths and kiosks is one of the largest in New York\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul class=\"content-list\">\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> Stand Up Style Booth</li>\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> Elite Style Booth</li>\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> Slow Motion Photo Booth</li>\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> Green Screen Station</li>\r\n 	<li><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> InstaPic Station</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhether it’s 2 or 12 guests trying to take a photo, it’s always more fun when they do it together. Often times a professional photographer can feel impersonal or make guests feel alienated or embarrassed. Having a destination—a photo booth—for your guests to make a trip to during the event is a fun distraction and excuse for groups to combine or separate. While waiting to take the photos your group are able to mingle and muse about the night’s events.\r\n<h3>Share Photos With Friends At The Party And Online</h3>\r\nThe instant satisfaction of prints is not only perfect for sharing on social media and friends at the party; it’s also fun and retro. Who doesn’t love an old black and white strip of photos to stick on the side of their bathroom mirror? If you’re looking to give your next event a little boost of goofy, lighthearted fun, you’ve come to the right place!\r\n<h3>Contact Us Today</h3>\r\nContact us at (888) 340-9190 to learn more about our photo booths or a complete list of kiosks. We can help you throw an unforgettable party or event. Reserve your photo booth today!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nISH Photo Booth Rental NY\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n84-64 169th St Jamaica\r\nCity: New York\r\nState: New York\r\nZip Code: 11432\r\n<a href=\"tel:8883409190\">Phone: (888) 340-9190</a>'),
