(2692, 422, 'photo_booth_rental_upper_content', '<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h2>Rent a Photo Booth</h2>\r\nISH Events is a full party photo booth rental company. Renting a photo booth is an exclusive and trendy means for your party celebration. We provide photo/<a title=\"Video Booths\" href=\"http://localhost/works/2019/11-nov/ish-photoboth-project/photoboth-wp/video-booth-service/\">video booths</a> with elegant design and high resolution studio quality photos that complement all events. Moreover, the fun ways of capturing quality pictures via photo booths rental services, serves as a perfect memento for your guests that clearly mark the occasion!\r\n\r\nWe offer our services in <a href=\"http://localhost/works/2019/11-nov/ish-photoboth-project/photoboth-wp/photo-booth-rentals-ny/\">New York</a>, <a href=\"http://localhost/works/2019/11-nov/ish-photoboth-project/photoboth-wp/photo-booth-rentals-nj/\">New Jersey</a>, <a href=\"http://localhost/works/2019/11-nov/ish-photoboth-project/photoboth-wp/photo-booth-rentals-ct/\">Connecticut</a> and Long Island., so you can get in touch with us to rent a photo booth for your special event or a party.\r\n\r\n</div>'),
