(2736, 69, 'default_template_content', '<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h2>Why Us</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class=\"content-list\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class=\"title\"><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> We guarantee the BEST PRICE!</p>\r\nWe will beat any price quote from any other real photo booth company.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class=\"title\"><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> We offer a real Arcade style photo booth. Our photo booth used to be set up in a mall.</p>\r\nBeware of other companies offering homemade photo booths. Beware of any photo booths made of paneling, all curtains or pipes and drapes.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class=\"title\"><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> We have the fastest and highest quality printer on the market.</p>\r\nWe use a sub-dye printer that prints in just 7 seconds. Since our printer is so fast more of your guests can use our photo booth. Our photos are high-quality so our photo strips can be submerged in water without the colors and ink running. High Quality means long lasting.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class=\"title\"><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> The Best most unique features on the market.</p>\r\nWe not only take high-quality fast photos. We can print strips for everyone so if 4 people take a photo all 4 get a copy. We can also print a 4x6 of your favorite photo. We can email the photos to your guests. Best of all we can collect a 30 second video message capturing those heart felt moments.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class=\"title\"><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> We can set up anywhere.</p>\r\nWe offer a real photo booth that can come apart. Our photo booth can go up stairs, through single doors and elevators.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class=\"title\"><i class=\"fa fa-hand-o-right\"></i> We guarantee to be the be best photo booth at the most afforable price.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>'),
