(2793, 424, 'scrap_booking_page_content', 'Our Scrap Book option is a really amazing memorable addition to our Photo Booth Rentals. Guests take photos in our booth. It prints an added copy. Our attendant puts that copy into a book. Shows your guests where to write a heartfelt message. We then put the book altogether in a nice organized way.\r\n\r\n<b>The Book is yours to Keep at the end of the event. </b>\r\n\r\nHard copies of every photo with heartfelt messages written next to each one. A really great way to remember your event forever.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"margin-top\"><b>This can be added to the following photo booths.</b></p>\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-camera\"></i> Stand up photo booth\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-camera\"></i> Traditional photo booth\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-camera\"></i> Elite photo booth\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-camera\"></i> Vertical photo station\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-camera\"></i> Mirror station\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-camera\"></i> Snap Chat Filter Station\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-camera\"></i> Instapic Station\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-camera\"></i> Photographer &amp; prints\r\n<div class=\"group-list btn-banner\"><a class=\"btn\">CUSTOMIZE YOUR PHOTO BOOTH EXPERIENCE TODAY!</a></div>'),
